1. *Ćerke* su mi najveća radost. (My daughters are my greatest joy.)
2. Oni imaju tri *ćerke*. (They have three daughters.)
3. Neke *ćerke* su se presele u drugu državu. (Some of the daughters have moved to another country.)
4. *Ćerka* mu je postala medicinska sestra. (His daughter became a nurse.)
5. U našoj porodici se sada nalaze četiri generacije: deda, roditelji, *ćerke* i unuke. (In our family there are now four generations: grandfather, parents, daughters and granddaughters.)